
'''= So Data! is a conference focused on the evolution of scientific practices impulsed by open science data.''' 

URL = http://sodata.org/


=Description=

"Open science data is a requirement for scientific reproducibility. It generates new research dynamics and promotes the pooling of scientific achievement all over the world including raw data, information and knowledge. So Data! invites researchers to share experiences around the use of open data in diverse scientific fields."


